window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They’ve exterminated an entire bloodline, purging the world of the only creatures vampires dread. Or so they think.</b></p> <p>Chloe used to study hard and do everything right to pave a bright future, but children sometimes have to pay for their parents’ sins, and Chloe’s tab is pretty steep. At 26, when a series of attacks forces her to seek refuge in the notorious Institute of Paranormal Studies, Chloe sees it as a second chance to achieve her goals. She believes she has nothing to lose. She couldn’t be more mistaken. </p> <p>Levi has had centuries to observe the mortals and immortals of this world. He knows what the sassy woman who entered his domain is at first glance. A relic of the old days...so ancient that even an elder lord descended from the first immortals has reason to fear her. </p> <p>He should slit her throat while he has the chance. </p> <p>He should.</p> <p><i>After Darkness Falls </i>is one in a series of stand-alone paranormal romance novels.</p>"; 
